31/05/2005
TIRANA, Albania -- President Alfred Moisiu met on Monday (30 May) with members of the Central Election Commission as part of preparations ahead of the 3 July parliamentary vote.
Moisiu called on the commission to ensure full implementation of the amended electoral code, and to act as an independent and responsible body before, during and after the vote.
Earlier this month, Moisiu met with representatives of the local government, the armed forces and the media.
(Albanian News - 31/05/05;
Albanian President Web site - 30/05/05)
